    1.1 silicon (LP: #1709123)
    - tty: pl011: fix initialization order of QDF2400 E44
  * Docker hangs with xfs using aufs storage driver (LP: #1709749)
    - SAUCE: aufs: for v4.5, use vfs_clone_file_range() in copy-up
